[b]RMB[/b] - [img=20x20]uid://dhhcof4kym2tu[/img] heavy attack
[b]E[/b] - [img=20x20]uid://dp87v6bn53hy5[/img] interact
[b]F[/b] - switch weapon
[b]Esc[/b] - pause
[/ul]
[hr color=web_gray]
